select 
program_key
,trim(cast(test_id  as char(255)))  as test_id
from $DO_GHL1_MY_MYSQL_FACT_TEST SRC_fact_test  force index (fact_test_test_id_Idx)
where
test_id >0
and STR_TO_DATE(CAST(SRC_fact_test.updated_on_date_key  AS CHAR(8)),'%Y%m%d')> DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL $SP_LOOK_BACK_DAYS.look_back_days DAY )
-- test_id in (50167811,50167851)
-- and STR_TO_DATE(CAST(SRC_fact_test.updated_on_date_key  AS CHAR(8)),'%Y%m%d')> DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL -10000 DAY )
group by
program_key
,trim(cast(test_id  as char(255)))

select 
program_key
,trim(cast(test_id  as char(255)))  as test_id
from $DO_GHL1_MY_MYSQL_FACT_RESULT SRC_fact_result  force index (fact_result_test_id_idx)

test_id >0
 and STR_TO_DATE(CAST( SRC_fact_result.result_created_at_date_key  AS CHAR(8)),'%Y%m%d')> DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL $SP_LOOK_BACK_DAYS.look_back_days DAY )

-- and STR_TO_DATE(CAST(SRC_fact_result.result_created_at_date_key   AS CHAR(8)),'%Y%m%d')> DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL -10000 DAY )
group by
program_key
,trim(cast(test_id  as char(255)))
